{"tid":269230,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"以填詞計 邊個要對香港樂壇衰亡負最大責任","createTime":"2017-06-03T15:17:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T22:32:17.000Z","uid":5584,"like":7,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dcbe17aeade929b42eb52c78e2f27f9731e834d3","tid":269230,"uid":5584,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T15:17:40.000Z","msg":"得罪講句，香港樂壇，最豐盛啦嘅年代，是影響整個華人社會，無論中國，東南亞，甚至遠至美國加拿大華人社區，都係聽我們香港出產的歌曲。當時我地香港係輸出香港的歌曲（及背後的文化）來感染全世界。<br />\n<br />\n但今時今日，我只見到全世界的歌曲（及背後的文化）湧入香港，反觀香港的歌曲，真係去到深圳都當你贏。<br />\n<br />\n既然隔離post話夕爺係神級填詞人，屌打哂其他填詞人，<span style=\"color: red;\">但係夕爺卻見証著整個樂壇嘅衰亡，咁我想問下以填詞計，夕爺係咪要對樂壇之死負最大責任？</span><br />\n<br />\n利申：我真係想拿出來討論，無意對夕爺不敬"},{"pid":"65aa812229d2408785d190bc2c49398a5d7ba3ae","tid":269230,"uid":27107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T15:42:03.000Z","msg":"佢做左d咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"410a58f6380ca8786c154da4abfac452e7ea6134","tid":269230,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T15:43:55.000Z","msg":"你講緊乜野"},{"pid":"258fd694ed9925511b6ca303cb0bba2159656c02","tid":269230,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T15:45:39.000Z","msg":"關夕爺咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d82e0949815526d8654f550e72a5874a04bbb7b","tid":269230,"uid":79171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T15:45:47.000Z","msg":"論證論據呢屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n擺低個論點就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n膠刀肺豉肶"},{"pid":"5f59af9e77a2e2c59c1adcbee66280825b1e3866","tid":269230,"uid":9672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T15:46:03.000Z","msg":"無人同你講野，都唔洗沖出嚟柒嘅你......"},{"pid":"2223a8763bd3aa88396fb1bc1d8657ce1b7024e1","tid":269230,"uid":5584,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T15:46:27.